org.usb4java

Class DeviceDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usb4java.DeviceDescriptor

  • public final class DeviceDescriptor
extends Object
    A structure representing the standard USB device descriptor. This descriptor is documented in section 9.6.1 of the USB 3.0 specification. All multiple-byte fields are represented in host-endian format.
    Author:
    Klaus Reimer (k@ailis.de)

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      DeviceDescriptor()
      Constructs a new device descriptor which can be passed to the LibUsb.getDeviceDescriptor(Device, DeviceDescriptor) method.
